    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v0 + 0.93 * tmp + 0.09)))
    v1 = (0.33 / wp.abs(tmp))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v1 + 0.53 - v2 + 0.09)))
    tmp = 0.89
    v2 = (0.50 * v2)
    tmp = 0.65
